author: HBO Max
description:
Chris Chalk (Dick Hallorann) joins Marc and Princess to unpack #ITWelcomeToDerry Episode Four, diving deep into Hallorann’s evolution as a reluctant seer and what it was like to step into such an iconic role. 

Then, John Bear Mitchell (Historical Consultant) shares how the creative team built the world of Derry on authentic Indigenous history, weaving the land’s real ancestral stories into the show’s mythology. We learn how themes of colonization, encroachment, and memory shaped Episode Four’s haunting backstory and why honoring the land’s spirit was essential to telling this tale right.
